
<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Grabaciones Eviternas — Catálogo</title>
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#d3c9b8;      /* beige similar al fondo de la imagen */
      --ink:#111;        /* texto principal */
      --accent:#b08a3a;  /* dorado */
      --card:#f4efe6;    /* tarjetas */
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html,body{margin:0;padding:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Ubuntu,Cantarell,Noto Sans,sans-serif;line-height:1.5}
    header{
      max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem 1rem 1rem 1rem;text-align:center
    }
    header img{
      width:min(520px,90vw);height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto 1rem;border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.18)
    }
    h1{font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.6rem);margin:.2rem 0 .5rem 0;letter-spacing:.5px}
    .kicker{display:inline-block;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;color:#fff;background:var(--ink);padding:.25rem .6rem;border-radius:999px;margin-bottom:.75rem}
    .lead{max-width:900px;margin:0 auto 1.25rem;font-size:1.05rem}
    .lead strong{color:var(--ink)}
    .badge{
      display:inline-block;margin:.2rem auto 1.25rem;padding:.35rem .75rem;border:1.5px solid var(--ink);border-radius:999px;font-weight:600;background:#fff0;backdrop-filter:blur(2px)
    }
    main{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1rem 4rem}
    h2{font-size:clamp(1.4rem,2.8vw,2rem);margin:1.25rem 0 .75rem}
    .grid{
      display:grid;gap:1rem;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));
    }
    .item{
      background:var(--card);border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);border-radius:16px;
      padding:1rem;box-shadow:0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.07);display:flex;flex-direction:column;
    }
    .item-image{
      width:100%;height:180px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:.75rem;cursor:pointer;transition:transform .2s ease,box-shadow .2s ease;
    }
    .item-image:hover{
      transform:scale(1.03);box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.15)
    }
    .item .title{font-weight:700;margin-bottom:.25rem}
    .item .meta{color:#333}
    .item .price{margin-top:.45rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)}
    .item.nuevo{position:relative}
    .item.nuevo::before{
      content:'NUEVO';position:absolute;top:10px;right:10px;background:var(--accent);color:#fff;padding:.2rem .5rem;border-radius:6px;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:700;z-index:1;
    }
    
    /* Modal */
    .modal{
      display:none;position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;background:rgba(0,0,0,.92);z-index:1000;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:1rem;
    }
    .modal.active{display:flex}
    .modal-content{
      max-width:90vw;max-height:90vh;position:relative;animation:zoomIn .3s ease;
    }
    .modal-content img{
      max-width:100%;max-height:90vh;object-fit:contain;border-radius:8px;
    }
    .modal-close{
      position:absolute;top:-40px;right:0;background:#fff;color:#111;border:none;width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;cursor:pointer;font-size:1.5rem;line-height:1;transition:background .2s;
    }
    .modal-close:hover{background:#f0f0f0}
    .modal-nav{
      position:absolute;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);background:rgba(255,255,255,.9);border:none;width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;cursor:pointer;font-size:1.5rem;transition:background .2s;
    }
    .modal-nav:hover{background:#fff}
    .modal-nav.prev{left:-60px}
    .modal-nav.next{right:-60px}
    .modal-nav:disabled{opacity:.3;cursor:not-allowed}
    @keyframes zoomIn{
      from{transform:scale(.8);opacity:0}
      to{transform:scale(1);opacity:1}
    }
    
    footer{
      text-align:center;padding:1.5rem;color:#222;border-top:1px dashed rgba(0,0,0,.25);background:#ece6da
    }
    .footer-link{
      color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;transition:color .2s;
    }
    .footer-link:hover{color:var(--ink)}
    
    @media(max-width:768px){
      .modal-nav{display:none}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <span class="kicker">Catálogo</span>
    <img src="GRABACIONES EVITERNAS.jpeg" alt="Grabaciones Eviternas — logotipo">
    <h1>Grabaciones Eviternas</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Ecos y vibraciones del <strong>darkwave</strong>, <strong>minimal synth</strong> y <strong>dark folk</strong> que trascienden el tiempo,
      tomando forma en vinilos y cassettes únicos a la venta y con entrega en <strong>CDMX</strong> o por envío.
    </p>
    <div class="badge">Merch disponible</div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <h2>Ediciones y Compilaciones</h2>
    <section class="grid" aria-label="Listado de artículos en venta">
      <article class="item">
        <div class="title">Accident Sentimental — So Solitaire</div>
        <div class="meta">Vinilo 12”</div>
        <div class="price">650 MXN</div>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <div class="title">Das Ding — Selected Archival Recordings 1979–1985</div>
        <div class="meta">Vinilo 12”</div>
        <div class="price">700 MXN</div>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <div class="title">FLO 926 — Dada Überall / La Bonne Heure</div>
        <div class="meta">Lathe Cut 7”</div>
        <div class="price">450 MXN</div>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <div class="title">La Merde — Kluitenbreker</div>
        <div class="meta">Cassette</div>
        <div class="price">250 MXN</div>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <div class="title">Larsovitch — NORMAL’NO</div>
        <div class="meta">Cassette</div>
        <div class="price">$300</div>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <div class="title">MAKiNA GiRGiR — Torment (2024)</div>
        <div class="meta">Vinilo 12”</div>
        <div class="price">750 MXN</div>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <div class="title">нат.аша — 666evil</div>
        <div class="meta">Cassette</div>
        <div class="price">300 MXN</div>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <div class="title">Ruinas para una Era Futura — Augurio / Visión</div>
        <div class="meta">Lathe Cut 7”</div>
        <div class="price">450 MXN</div>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <div class="title">V.A. — Tower of Light & Hearts of Stone (Compilación 1)</div>
        <div class="meta">Cassette</div>
        <div class="price">$300</div>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <div class="title">V.A. — The Chapel of Visions (Compilación 2)</div>
        <div class="meta">Cassette</div>
        <div class="price">$300</div>
      </article>

      <article class="item">
        <div class="title">V.A. — Songs from the Phantom Ship (Compilación 3)</div>
        <div class="meta">Cassette</div>
        <div class="price">$300</div>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    AEviternAE 2025
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
